  "content": "<p>Maquis fighters are members of the French Resistance who are actively resisting the German occupation of France.</p>\n<p>Maquis fighters (also known as Maquisards) work closely with foreign operatives to infiltrate occupied territory and</p>\n<p>conduct sabotage, reconnaissance, and assassination missions.</p>\n<p>Maquis fighters have numerous contacts and rely heavily on the support of the local French populace.</p>\n<p>Maquis fighters are masters of guerilla tactics, using concealment and cover to ambush and harass German forces whenever possible.</p>\n<h2>Advancement</h2>\n<table style=\"width: 503px; border-style: solid; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; height: 107px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 27px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>Level</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;XP</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;HD</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;BHB</h3>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; text-align: center; height: 27px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;ST</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1 + 1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">15</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1250</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">14</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2500</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">3 + 1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">13</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 96px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 84px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">10000</td>\n<td style=\"width: 87px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 114px; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">11</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Abilities</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Cobble</li>\n<li>Conceal Items</li>\n<li>Contacts</li>\n<li>Resistance Leader (3rd level)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br />Saving Throws</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Maquis characters impose a <strong>-2 penalty </strong>to all Saving Throws made to detect when they are being deceptive.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><br />XP Bonus</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Maquis characters with a Wisdom of 13 or 14 receive a 5% Experience Bonus, and those with 15 or higher get 10%.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"
